### ============================================
### Testing Script — API IoT GEMA Imam
### ============================================
### Cara pakai:
###   - Jika pakai VS Code: Install extension "REST Client"
###     lalu klik "Send Request" di atas tiap blok.
###   - Jika pakai Postman/curl: Salin endpoint, header, dan body.
###
### Ganti variabel di bawah sesuai environment kamu:
###   @baseUrl    = URL server Next.js
###   @apiKey     = IOT_SECRET_KEY dari .env.local
###   @imamId     = UUID imam dari tabel imams (hasil SQL migration)
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@apiKey = gema-iot-secret-2026

### -----------------------------------------------
### 1. Mulai Sesi Sholat
### -----------------------------------------------
### Ganti imam_id dengan UUID asli dari tabel imams di Supabase.

POST {{baseUrl}}/iot/sesi/mulai
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "imam_id": "GANTI_DENGAN_UUID_IMAM",
  "nama_sholat": "Dhuhur",
  "timestamp": "2026-07-13T12:00:00Z"
}

### Response yang diharapkan:
### {
###   "success": true,
###   "sesi_id": "c9e2b10a-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx"
### }

### -----------------------------------------------
### 2. Kirim Log Gerakan
### -----------------------------------------------
### Ganti sesi_id dengan nilai dari response step 1.

POST {{baseUrl}}/iot/gerakan
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "sesi_id": "GANTI_DENGAN_SESI_ID",
  "rakaat": 1,
  "nama_gerakan": "rukuk",
  "entry_time": "12:01:05",
  "exit_time": "12:01:10",
  "duration_seconds": 5.0,
  "tumaninah_terpenuhi": true,
  "gerakan_menyimpang": [],
  "hip_angle": 88.5,
  "knee_angle": 175.2,
  "arm_angle": 12.0,
  "foto_pose_url": ""
}

### Response yang diharapkan:
### {
###   "success": true,
###   "message": "Gerakan tersimpan"
### }

### -----------------------------------------------
### 3. Selesai Sesi Sholat
### -----------------------------------------------
### Ganti sesi_id dengan nilai dari response step 1.

POST {{baseUrl}}/iot/sesi/selesai
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "sesi_id": "GANTI_DENGAN_SESI_ID",
  "status": "Selesai",
  "durasi_detik": 245.0,
  "total_rakaat": 4,
  "total_kesalahan_imam": 1,
  "skor_tumaninah_persen": 85.5
}

### Response yang diharapkan:
### {
###   "success": true,
###   "message": "Sesi sholat ditutup"
### }

### -----------------------------------------------
### 4. Upload Foto Pose (Multipart)
### -----------------------------------------------
### Catatan: REST Client VS Code mendukung multipart.
### Jika pakai Postman, set Body → form-data → key "file" (type: File).

POST {{baseUrl}}/iot/media/upload
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test_pose.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test_pose.jpg
------FormBoundary--

### Response yang diharapkan:
### {
###   "success": true,
###   "url": "https://res.cloudinary.com/xxx/image/upload/v1234/gema_imam_poses/abc123.jpg"
### }

### -----------------------------------------------
### 5. Test Unauthorized (Tanpa API Key)
### -----------------------------------------------
### Seharusnya gagal dengan 401.

POST {{baseUrl}}/iot/sesi/mulai
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imam_id": "test",
  "nama_sholat": "Subuh"
}

### Response yang diharapkan:
### {
###   "success": false,
###   "error": "Unauthorized — API key tidak valid"
### }
